  &lt;h4&gt;The Bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
          DOGE fires entire staff at Institute of Museum and Library Services &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/03/31/nx-s1-5334415/doge-institute-of-museum-and-library-services&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
