          Social Security Administration collapse is beginning &lt;a href=&quot;https://finance.yahoo.com/news/social-security-website-crashes-agency-212827914.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
