              &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Signal chat post from Pete Hegseth: TEAM UPDATE: TIME NOW (1144et): Weather is FAVORABLE. Just CONFIRMED w/ CENTCOM we are a GO for mission launch. 1215et: F-18s LAUNCH (1st strike package). 1345: &#39;Trigger Based&#39; F-18 1st Strike Window Starts (Target Terrorist is @ his Known Location so SHOULD BE ON TIME) - also, Strike Drones Launch (MQ-9s). 1410: More F-18s LAUNCH (2nd strike package). 1415: Strike Drones on Target (THIS IS WHEN THE FIRST BOMBS WILL DEFINITELY DROP, pending earlier &#39;Trigger Based&#39; targets). 1536: &amp;amp;-18 2nd Strike Starts - also, first sea-based Tomahawks launched.&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;/images/hyNQjwvQjI-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;274&quot;&gt;
