  &lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
          If we deport all the immigrants, who will take their jobs? Our children! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/miami/news/desantis-backs-bill-loosening-child-labor-laws-amid-immigration-crackdown/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
