          Venezuelans deported to torture center for no better reason than because they had tattoos &lt;a href=&quot;https://truthout.org/articles/report-trump-admin-deported-venezuelan-men-just-because-they-had-tattoos/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
