                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thelongmemo.com/p/every-student-loan-is-now-forgiven&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(The Long Memo) Every student loan is now &quot;forgiven&quot; thanks to Trump&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
