                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://taxfoundation.org/research/all/federal/trump-tariffs-trade-war/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Tax Foundation) Trump Tariffs: Tracking the economic impact of the Trump trade war&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
