        The numbers are in: Republicans&#39; tax cuts steal from the poor to give to the rich &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/trump-budget-analysis-take-from-poor-b2718333.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
