          &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;
            &lt;a href=&quot;https://runforsomething.net/run/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;
              &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;A woman in a crowd shows what she is writing on a piece of paper to a man watches with interest&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;/images/HwL0xvrc4S-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;299&quot;&gt;
            &lt;/a&gt;
              &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com/users/surprising_snapshots-11873433/?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=9079706&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Mircea Iancu&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com//?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=9079706&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Pixabay&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;It&#39;s easy to complain about those who are supposed to represent our interests in the government. But do you think you have what it takes to do better? Learn how to run for local office, and get the support and encouragement you need to &quot;Run for something.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;This organization lowers the barriers to entry for starting a career as a civil servant, and provides guidance, assistance, and visibility along the way.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;So go ahead...Run for something!&lt;/p&gt;
