            Democrats fill void left by Republicans hiding from constituents &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wkow.com/news/politics/rep-mark-pocan-draws-packed-crowd-at-town-hall-meeting-calls-out-rep-derrick-van/article_d66c5c3e-fc84-11ef-8623-5fd46eda89b2.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link &lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
