&lt;h4&gt;What can you do in the week ahead?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;table table-transparent table-shadow&quot;&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td width=&quot;200px&quot; class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;
        &lt;a href=&quot;https://indivisible.org/resource/call-now-tell-your-representative-vote-no-save-act&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;
          &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Indivisible Logo&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;/images/rlTC3hsjYJ-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;200&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
          Connect to your representative
        &lt;/a&gt;
      &lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;House Republicans are pushing a bill, called the SAVE Act that intends to disenfranchise millions of eligible American voters.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Under the guise of election security, the SAVE Act would require proof of citizenship to be presented to register to vote. When that&#39;s all you hear, it sounds very reasonable. But there are problems with this:&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;Not everyone can access these documents (They are frequently lost or destroyed)&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;They must be presented in person, eliminating online and mail-in voter registration&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;It would prevent most married women from being able to register to vote if they changed their names when they married&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;It makes it easier to intimidate and add barriers to naturalized citizens&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;It just makes it harder in general, so fewer people will register to vote&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Indivisible has an &lt;a href=&quot;https://indivisible.org/resource/call-now-tell-your-representative-vote-no-save-act&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online form&lt;/a&gt; you can fill out to get connected directly to your representative so you can tell them to vote NO on this dangerous bill.&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;  
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://events.pol-rev.com/@50501_movement/events&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;
