            &lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin-left:0.5rem&quot;&gt;
              &lt;b&gt;&quot;Republicans [are] just eating it in their home districts and their home states as their party&#39;s leader does things that are devestating to those states and to those constituents.&quot;&lt;/b&gt;
            &lt;/blockquote&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/td&gt;
